about.summary: Ultra fast JSON decoder and encoder written in C with Python bindings

name: ujson
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ujson" %}
{% set version = "1.35" %}
{% set sha256 = "f66073e5506e91d204ab0c614a148d5aa938bdbf104751be66f8ad7a222f5f86" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 1001
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - ujson

about:
  home: https://github.com/esnme/ultrajson
  summary: "Ultra fast JSON decoder and encoder written in C with Python bindings"
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.txt'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kszucs
